Version 0.3.2
-------------

Released on December ?th, 2012

* add nadir hotspot
* make autoration smarter
* make use of FullScreener and LinkOpener SaladoPlayer modules
* make use of ImageMap SaladoPlayer modules
* make use of Compass SaladoPlayer modules
* remove custom fields in data model so that south can be used again

Version 0.3.1
-------------

Released on December 15th, 2012

* display photo galleries using SaladoPlayer module Gallery and the Django application Photologue
* take the hotspot images from a Photologue gallery
* add a management command (spinit) for initializing Django-saladoplayer (automatically create the above gallery)
* use the zoom slider module
* add screen shots in the documentation
* update the documentation
* update the SaladoPlayer modules

Version 0.3.0
-------------

Released on December 2nd, 2012

* use django-photologue for managing photos and galleries

Version 0.2.4
-------------

Released on December 2ndth, 2012

* access a tour via an identifier (slug of the title) in the url
* added meta information for displaying the tour in facebook

Version 0.2.3
-------------

Released on November 5th, 2012

* corrected a bug in the many2many relationship between panoramas

Version 0.2.2
-------------

Released on November 3rd, 2012

* added a template for standalone viewing of panorama tour
* updated MenuScroller and LensFlare modules

Version 0.2.1
-------------

Released on October 20th, 2012

* the viewfinder is now avaiable as a field in the tour data model instead of a general configuration

Version 0.2
-----------

Released on October 19th, 2012

* added dropDownMenu feature
* added initial camera position
* added vertical angle limitation
* added auto rotation
* updated swf saladopayer modules

Version 0.1.2
-------------

Released on October 16th, 2012

* correct initial panorama in xml configuration file template
* correct doc typos

Version 0.1.1
-------------

Released on July 7th, 2012

* correct some typos in docs and docstrings
* add a tips file in doc
* update SaladoPLayer modules to SaladoPlayer-1.3.2
* prevents easy_install from zipping the package in an egg file (templates files must be present in the filesystem)

